{"tid":2295593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：不排除推更嚴厲防疫措施令粵澳放心 盡早恢復三地通關","createTime":"2020-11-22T02:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T08:11:14.000Z","uid":50386,"like":51,"dislike":224,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"7998fd5e5baa1731557c37eca0706b92542f3635","tid":2295593,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗今在網誌撰文表示，近日本港疫情急速惡化，形勢急轉，來勢洶洶，呼籲市民加強自律和自我保護，減少非必要的外出和聚會，嚴格遵守各處所的防疫規定和限制。特區政府正嚴陣以待，不排除推出更嚴厲的防疫措施遏制疫情，令粵澳及內地當局對香港放心，務能盡早逐步有序地恢復三地通關，重啟本港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201122/KUGJOQK2HFDATGFJYAOAR5ZY3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201122%2FKUGJOQK2HFDATGFJYAOAR5ZY3E%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5ryVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=100a4545\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201122%2FKUGJOQK2HFDATGFJYAOAR5ZY3E%2F&h=db0d9e32\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201122/KUGJOQK2HFDATGFJYAOAR5ZY3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n只許支那人來港<br />\n不許香港人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c109622bc612296b178b0b83111f49f82ddba3e6","tid":2295593,"uid":41087,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:11:45.000Z","msg":"仲唔死心 日日諗住開關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a2e8f6d78c3d560e7ddc28ee4afad941ad670f","tid":2295593,"uid":230530,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:12:25.000Z","msg":"大陸官員都話佢自私"},{"pid":"6d7b84f4963f9b9d0cc43f05325a10494e423673","tid":2295593,"uid":366470,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"香港政府唔係想令香港人放心<br />\n而係令支國同澳門放心?<br />\n咩邏輯"},{"pid":"020f49a3f5b1e260209cafc2056d27c6d617de48","tid":2295593,"uid":126648,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"c109622bc612296b178b0b83111f49f82ddba3e6","tid":2295593,"uid":41087,"like":118,"dislike":0,